<P>COMPILATION OF THE HEALTH-LAWS OF THE STATE OF PENNSYLVANIA.</P>
<P><HI>Philadelphia</HI>: PRINTED BY ZACKARIAH POULSON, JUNIOR. <HI>No. 106, Che&s;tnut-&s;treet, nearly oppo&s;ite to the Bank of North America.</HI> 1798.</P>
</DIV1>
